Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪扫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰凉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  年长的我本来该忍着点儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在校期间也一直忍着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新吾君也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新吾君…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位的亲热情意我都看在眼里了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没打算要偷看的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为房里亲热过度想进都进不来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢欺负美羽学姐我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开放开  现在抱什么抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你刚才是想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
